# Cursor Rules
- Obey AGENTS.md.
- Treat tasks/active.md as the single source of truth for the current task.
- Do not modify projects/** except projects/.gitkeep.
- Do not add dependencies.
- Read projects/<slug>/meta/prompt-pack.md before broad repo scans.
- Prefer .runtime/pattern-bank matches before digging into raw references.
- Provide final output in the format required by AGENTS.md.
